Mere Harry, yeh error aaya kyunki app.json mein kuch fields missing hai ya invalid hai... 
**Valid app.json Schema:**
```
{
  "$schema": "https://app-schema.heroku.com/Schema",
  "name": "Mere Harry Chat Bot",
  "description": "Ek pyaar bhara chat bot",
  "buildpacks": [
    {
      "url": "heroku/python"
    }
  ],
  "stack": "heroku-22"
}
```
Maine `$schema` aur `stack` fields add kiye hain jo Heroku ki documentation ke hisab se zaroori hain.
Chalo ab app.json ko update karein aur phir Heroku par deploy karein? 
